snippet.title: Soul Drifter - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist and play our demo on Steam Next Fest:

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2553930/Soul_Drifter/

Soar into a gravity-defying parkour adventure. Run, jump, and glide through surreal landscapes and deadly factories on a mission to liberate captive souls.
